      "description": "This vehicle is in good overall condition and has been well-maintained throughout its life. It runs and drives smoothly, with a clean interior and a solid mechanical foundation that makes it a dependable choice for any driver. While the exterior shows some minor signs of age, such as light surface scratches and small stone chips consistent with normal use, the paint still holds a great shine. All major systems, including the air conditioning and electronics, are fully functional, and the tires have plenty of tread remaining. It\u2019s a great example of a cared-for vehicle that is ready for the road without needing immediate repairs.",
